{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/ciayo-comics-rewards-program/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Ngomik di CIAYO Comics Bisa Dapat Poin dan Hadiah!","content":"<p>Buat kamu yang baca <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/dicari-ceo-ciayo-comics-untuk-sehari/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">CIAYO Comics</a> lewat <em>app smartphone</em> atau <em>website</em>, nyadar nggak ada sesuatu yang berbeda dengan tampilannya? Yap, mulai sekarang, CIAYO Comics punya program super keren buat para pembaca setia dan juga <em>author</em> CIAYO Comics, yang namanya CIAYO Comics REWARDS!</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_50701\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-50701\" data-attachment-id=\"50701\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/ciayo-comics-rewards-program/attachment/01-ciayo-comics-reward/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/01-ciayo-comics-reward.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"01-ciayo-comics-reward\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/01-ciayo-comics-reward-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/01-ciayo-comics-reward.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-50701\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/01-ciayo-comics-reward.jpg\" alt=\"CIAYO Comics rewards\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/01-ciayo-comics-reward.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/01-ciayo-comics-reward-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-50701\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: CIAYO Comics</p></div></p>\n<p>CIAYO Comics REWARDS adalah program terbaru di CIAYO Comics sebagai bentuk apresiasi buat kamu pembaca setia dan para <em>author</em> CIAYO Comics. Sekarang baca komik di CIAYO Comics ada hadiahnya loh! Tapi ada syaratnya, yaitu kamu harus buktiin kalau kamu adalah fans setia komik-komik CIAYO Comics lewat serangkaian kuis dan <em>challenge</em>.</p>\n<p>Penasaran seperti apa <em>challenge</em>-nya? Apa aja yang bisa kamu dapat di CIAYO Comics REWARDS? Ikuti tata caranya di bawah ini!</p>\n<h2>Cara Main CIAYO Comics REWARDS</h2>\n<h3>1. Login/Buat Akun CIAYO Comics</h3>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_50702\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-50702\" data-attachment-id=\"50702\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/ciayo-comics-rewards-program/attachment/02-ciayo-comics-reward/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/02-ciayo-comics-reward.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"02-ciayo-comics-reward\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/02-ciayo-comics-reward-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/02-ciayo-comics-reward.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-50702\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/02-ciayo-comics-reward.jpg\" alt=\"CIAYO Comics rewards\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/02-ciayo-comics-reward.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/02-ciayo-comics-reward-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-50702\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: CIAYO Comics</p></div></p>\n<p>Tahap pertama sebelum ikut CIAYO Comics REWARDS, kamu harus punya akun CIAYO Comics dulu. Kalau sudah punya, tinggal <em>login</em> saja dengan akun kamu. Kalau belum, buruan bikin! Dengan akun CIAYO Comics, kamu bisa simpan semua <em>subscribe</em> komik kamu dan ikut komentar di komik serta <em>author</em> favorit kamu.</p>\n<p>Kamu bisa <em>login</em> dan buat akun CIAYO Comics dengan mengklik tombol <strong>Login/Register</strong> di kanan atas layar.</p>\n<h3>2. Buka Halaman CIAYO Comics REWARDS</h3>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_50703\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-50703\" data-attachment-id=\"50703\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/ciayo-comics-rewards-program/attachment/03-ciayo-comics-reward/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/03-ciayo-comics-reward.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"03-ciayo-comics-reward\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/03-ciayo-comics-reward-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/03-ciayo-comics-reward.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-50703\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/03-ciayo-comics-reward.jpg\" alt=\"CIAYO Comics rewards\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/03-ciayo-comics-reward.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/03-ciayo-comics-reward-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-50703\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: CIAYO Comics</p></div></p>\n<p>Kalau sudah <em>login</em>, kamu bisa akses halaman CIAYO Comics REWARDS di <a href=\"https://rewards.ciayo.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">http://rewards.ciayo.com</a> atau dengan mengklik <em>banner</em> CIAYO Comics REWARDS di halaman depan. Di halaman ini, kamu bisa cek jumlah <strong>point</strong> kamu dan ikut kuis harian. Untuk cek point kamu, klik tombol <strong>My Point</strong> di kanan atas layar. Untuk mulai kuis harian, klik tombol <strong>Start Today’s Trivia</strong>.</p>\n<h3>3. Jawab 5 Pertanyaan Setiap Harinya</h3>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_50704\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-50704\" data-attachment-id=\"50704\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/ciayo-comics-rewards-program/attachment/04-ciayo-comics-reward/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/04-ciayo-comics-reward.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"04-ciayo-comics-reward\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/04-ciayo-comics-reward-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/04-ciayo-comics-reward.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-50704\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/04-ciayo-comics-reward.jpg\" alt=\"CIAYO Comics rewards\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/04-ciayo-comics-reward.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/04-ciayo-comics-reward-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-50704\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: CIAYO Comics</p></div></p>\n<p>Setelah mengklik tombol <strong>Start Today’s Trivia</strong>, kamu akan diberikan 5 pertanyaan dengan pilihan ganda. Pertanyaannya nggak serumit Ujian Nasional, kok! Kalau kamu baca komik-komiknya CIAYO Comics, yakin deh semuanya bisa kamu jawab dengan tepat! Cukup klik jawaban yang menurut kamu tepat, dan nanti hasilnya akan muncul.</p>\n<p>Setiap pertanyaan yang benar akan mendapatkan 20 point, dengan total point maksimal yang bisa kamu dapatkan per harinya adalah 100 point. Untuk setiap jawaban yang benar, point yang didapat akan diakumulasikan untuk ditambah ke dalam koleksi point kamu. Untuk dapat lebih banyak point, jawab kembali kuisnya besok dan seterusnya sampai kamu mendapatkan point sebanyak yang kamu mau.</p>\n<h3>4. Tukar Point Dengan Hadiah!</h3>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_50705\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-50705\" data-attachment-id=\"50705\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/ciayo-comics-rewards-program/attachment/05-ciayo-comics-reward/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/05-ciayo-comics-reward.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"05-ciayo-comics-reward\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/05-ciayo-comics-reward-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/05-ciayo-comics-reward.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-50705\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/05-ciayo-comics-reward.jpg\" alt=\"CIAYO Comics rewards\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/05-ciayo-comics-reward.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/05-ciayo-comics-reward-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-50705\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: CIAYO Comics</p></div></p>\n<p>Jika sudah punya point cukup, kamu bisa menukar point dengan mengklik tombol <strong>Redeem</strong> di sisi atas layar atau di layar hasil kuis. Kamu bisa menukar point kamu dengan berbagai macam hadiah; mulai dari <strong><em>voucher</em> Go-Pay</strong>, <strong>tiket film</strong>, serta berbagai <strong><em>merchandise</em> CIAYO Comics</strong>! Hadiah lain akan ditambahkan, jadi terus cek siapa tahu ada <em>swag</em> incaran edisi terbatas!</p>\n<p>Dan buat kamu pembaca setia CIAYO Comics, kamu bakal dapat <strong>bonus 500 point</strong> begitu kamu mendaftarkan akun CIAYO Comics! Mantap, kan?</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_50706\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-50706\" data-attachment-id=\"50706\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/ciayo-comics-rewards-program/attachment/06-ciayo-comics-reward/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/06-ciayo-comics-reward.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"06-ciayo-comics-reward\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/06-ciayo-comics-reward-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/06-ciayo-comics-reward.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-50706\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/06-ciayo-comics-reward.jpg\" alt=\"CIAYO Comics rewards\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/06-ciayo-comics-reward.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/06-ciayo-comics-reward-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-50706\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: CIAYO Comics</p></div></p>\n<h2>Author Juga Bisa Ikutan!</h2>\n<p>Nggak cuma pembaca CIAYO Comics aja yang bisa ikutan CIAYO Comics REWARDS, <em>author</em> CIAYO Comics juga bisa ikutan! <em>Author</em> CIAYO Comics bisa ikut menyelesaikan kuis dan <em>challenge</em> yang lebih banyak dan lebih menantang. Karena jauh lebih menantang, point yang didapatkan jauh lebih banyak, dan hadiah yang bisa didapatkan <em>author</em> pun lebih menarik! Ada <strong>buku impor</strong>, <strong><em>marker</em> Copic</strong>, <strong><em>headphone</em></strong>, hingga <strong><em>drawing tablet</em></strong>!</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_50707\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-50707\" data-attachment-id=\"50707\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/updates/ciayo-comics-rewards-program/attachment/07-ciayo-comics-reward/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/07-ciayo-comics-reward.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"07-ciayo-comics-reward\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/07-ciayo-comics-reward-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/07-ciayo-comics-reward.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-50707\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/07-ciayo-comics-reward.jpg\" alt=\"CIAYO Comics rewards\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/07-ciayo-comics-reward.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/09/07-ciayo-comics-reward-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-50707\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: CIAYO Comics</p></div></p>\n<p>Tahapan-tahapan yang harus dijalani oleh <em>author</em> tidak jauh berbeda dengan pembaca CIAYO Comics. <em>Login</em> ke akun CIAYO Comics, buka <a href=\"https://rewards.ciayo.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">https://rewards.ciayo.com/</a>, selesaikan setiap <em>challenge,</em> dan tukar point-nya.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe style=\"border: none; overflow: hidden;\" src=\"https://www.facebook.com/plugins/video.php?href=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fciayocom%2Fvideos%2F1140077642809091%2F&amp;show_text=0&amp;width=476\" width=\"476\" height=\"476\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\n<p>Jadi tunggu apa lagi? Segera buka CIAYO Comics dan baca komik-komik favorit kamu agar kans kemenangan kamu semakin besar! Klik gambar di bawah untuk mulai <a href=\"https://www.ciayo.com/id\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">baca komik online</a> di CIAYO Comics.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.ciayo.com/id/comic\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img data-attachment-id=\"50176\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/manga-terpopuler-di-indonesia-pada-2018/attachment/print-7/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/Banner-Home-CIAYO-Comics.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1534766427&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Print&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Banner Halaman CIAYO Comics id\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/Banner-Home-CIAYO-Comics-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/Banner-Home-CIAYO-Comics.jpg\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-50176\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/Banner-Home-CIAYO-Comics.jpg\" alt=\"Baca komik online di CIAYO Comics\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/Banner-Home-CIAYO-Comics.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/Banner-Home-CIAYO-Comics-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /></a></p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"04a626d6-2168-5a54-8b13-b6ef34055af2"}}}